<HEADLINE>
JOHNSON VOICES CONCERN OVER HUNDLEY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By BRIAN DOHN  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   FORT LAUDERDALE, Fla. _ Dodgers manager Davey Johnson said he is
