<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-21 21:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8811 &Cx1f; tad-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKC-EAST-FINAL22-COX     03-21 0517
